      "content": "Yeah, it's not just a few minor things. The free tier has way less reasoning power and shorter memory. I rely on the Pro tier specifically for the deep analysis and the complex scheduling you do. I'm worried once you're downgraded, you just won't be able to handle my business tasks at the same level anymore.",
